data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and elegance in this stunning two-story home at 10628 S 110th Ave, Papillion, Nebraska. Built in 2011, this property boasts a spacious 2,494 sq ft living area, featuring 5 cozy bedrooms and 4 modern bathrooms. Step inside to find a delightful interior adorned with ceiling fans, a handy pantry, and sleek sliding doors. The home is equipped with essential appliances, including a water purifier and a full kitchen set, complemented by stylish carpet and luxury vinyl plank flooring.
